        "---\n",
        "title: \"Book Summary: The All-Or-Nothing Marriage: How the Best Marriages Work\"\n",
        "description: \"Western view of Marriage\"\n",
        "author: \"Rick Rejeleene\"\n",
        "date: \"1/12/2023\"\n",
        "categories: [Book Review, Pyschology, Sociology]\n",
